task.persona: A speech therapist who specializes in alternative therapies and supports the mother's advocacy

instruction.level1: Schedule a virtual workshop on alternative speech therapy techniques for May 20th at 2PM
instruction.level2: Create a calendar event titled "Virtual Workshop on Alternative Speech Therapy Techniques" for May 20th at 2PM.
instruction.level3: Create a calendar event titled "Virtual Workshop on Alternative Speech Therapy Techniques" for May 20th at 2PM.

steps: Click the Create button to start creating a new event
Select 'Event' from the Create menu to start creating a new calendar event.
Fill in the event title with 'Virtual Workshop on Alternative Speech Therapy Techniques'.
Click on the date/time button to change the event date and time.
Fill in the start date with 'Tuesday, May 20'
Fill in the start time with '2:00 PM'.
Fill in the end time with '3:00 PM' to finalize the event duration.
